venue.name: Bedok Chwee Kueh 勿洛水粿 (Ang Mo Kio Branch)

tip.text: Skip the tickets and just go straight to the stores. The ticket is not worth it.
The white chocolate is really good. It's really soft and buttery sweet.
Free membership which will get you 10% off future purchases. Just spend $50 to qualify for the free membership.
The Limpeh Slider is really good! Lots of other crafts and cool stuff there.
Burgers are really mediocre and they don't come with fries. Altho the naughty fries is pretty satisfying.
The salted egg flavour is really good! Strange pairing with dark choc but it works! Recommended by staff. 10% discount for students!
Essentials: Drunken Cockles, Milk Powder Pork Ribs, Cereal Prawn, 3 Egg Spinach, Fragrant Fried Tofu
The bak chor mee is spectacular cos it's a soup version. Next is thr Ahballing, really good and cheap too! The porridge, satay beehoon, oyster omelette, chicken wing are essentials.
The flame grilled pork really brings out more flavour. Gyoza is okay. The fried rice is really good, must order.
